  "body": "# ðŸ’Ž Issue\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nIn #9390, @kasey brought up the fact that special casing metadata in https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/develop/beacon-chain/p2p/sender.go#L36 is brittle and requires us to hardcode \r\nspecial cases for it everywhere. A better method would be to refactor `Send` to allow us to simply open a stream without encoding anything over. This would allow us to remove the brittle harcoded checks that we have for metadata currently.  ",
